    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "If you're not using the chat component (which I guess isn't the case on react native), you can indeed force those dependencies to be aliased to a version that works for you, or an entirely empty package.\n\nAs this is downstream, we can't do that much about it right now, but will look into checking if making ai more optional could be possible.",
